snippet: Abby Wambach scored on a diving header in the 51st minute, and the United States women’s soccer team beat Scotland in a friendly in Nashville. The game was Wambach’s 200th international match.
lead_paragraph: Abby Wambach scored on a diving header in the 51st minute, and the United States women’s soccer team beat Scotland in a friendly in Nashville. The game was Wambach’s 200th international match.
